# For full functionality, use one of these approaches instead:
#   1. Access UniFi directly at https://homenetwork.com:8443
#   2. Use a dedicated subdomain: https://unifi.homenetwork.com (root path proxy)
#   3. Use a dedicated server block that proxies / to UniFi
#
# This subpath configuration (/{{ unifi_nginx_path }}) will have limited functionality
